Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.39,0:01:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Otani...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.29,0:01:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.66,0:01:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to have to take back that "Let's pretend nothing happened."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.60,0:01:31.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I still like you, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.83,0:01:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Just keep that in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.98,0:01:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,'Kay.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.96,0:01:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I like who I like.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.02,0:01:56.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You got a problem with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.47,0:02:07.24,Title,,0,0,0,,A Confrontation With the Ex-Girlfriend?!\NThe Great Chest Baring Plan!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.51,0:02:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.71,0:02:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been cut off!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.61,0:02:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Pretty lame, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.28,0:02:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously, Umibouzu's wife, couldn't you have done better?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.88,0:02:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, here's another picture of you looking lame.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.85,0:02:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What? There are more?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.55,0:02:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.39,0:02:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Gimme that!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.12,0:02:31.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Why should I? I took it using my own camera.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.26,0:02:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,No good will come of you having that picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.40,0:02:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I could print out a few more copies and put them up in the hallway.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.00,0:02:39.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll hit you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.20,0:02:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that how you treat the guy you like?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.24,0:02:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you have to say stuff like that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.84,0:02:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It's your fault, no matter how you look at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.91,0:02:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I'm definitely gonna print more copies!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.75,0:02:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll make a hundred copies and hand them out with tissues in front of the station.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.35,0:02:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I really will hit you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.48,0:02:57.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Go ahead, if you dare.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.59,0:03:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,The data is still stored in my camera, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.16,0:03:01.16,Overlap,,0,0,0,,They're back to normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.16,0:03:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,A little too normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.09,0:03:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,This is bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.06,0:03:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Otani knows my biggest weakness now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.13,0:03:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,This is making me mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.13,0:03:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't the time to get mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.03,0:03:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you were going to make Otani-kun regret rejecting you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.67,0:03:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,That's easier said than done.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.01,0:03:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Nevertheless, don't make that ugly face!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.88,0:03:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Think. Why did he reject you in the first place?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.01,0:03:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It was because he thinks of you as his comedy partner, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.45,0:03:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.52,0:03:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.49,0:03:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't just keep doing comedy with him like before.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.96,0:03:34.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Use your seductiveness! Seductiveness!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.19,0:03:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,"Seductiveness"?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.19,0:03:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly, bare your chest completely and move forward!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.53,0:03:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,How can I do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.33,0:03:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Then do a lap of the station area!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.73,0:03:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be arrested!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.73,0:03:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean show that kind of attitude!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.40,0:03:46.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.40,0:03:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What the heck is a "chest baring attitude"?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.18,0:03:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Christmas again.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.62,0:04:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,A year sure goes by quickly, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.29,0:04:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What, are you an old woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.19,0:04:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.86,0:04:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,...last Christmas, he blew off his ex-girlfriend and kept me company.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.36,0:04:16.97,Default,,0,0,0,,She sure was cute...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.74,0:04:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey Otani...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.54,0:04:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What was your relationship with Kanzaki-san like?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.67,0:04:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with this all of a sudden?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.94,0:04:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It would bother anyone in my position.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.88,0:04:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It was normal. Normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.88,0:04:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Normal, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.75,0:04:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.65,0:04:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.82,0:04:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Well you guys weren't ever a comedy duo, were you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.56,0:04:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,The girl Otani went out with...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.86,0:04:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The girl he liked...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.87,0:04:53.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to become the girl that Otani likes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.77,0:04:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,How should I do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.01,0:05:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What should I give my darling for Christmas?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.18,0:05:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Chiharu-chan, what are you going to give Suzuki-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.71,0:05:06.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, last year I gave him a sweater...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.69,0:05:12.39,Default,,0,0,0,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.39,0:05:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine. Don't mind me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.16,0:05:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Risa, you don't have any plans for Christmas this year, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.10,0:05:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,So what?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.43,0:05:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you ask Otani-kun out?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.03,0:05:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell him you want to spend Christmas eve together, just the two of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.77,0:05:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.80,0:05:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,He rejected me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.37,0:05:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way I could say something so embarrassing!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.47,0:05:34.41,Default,,0,0,0,,He already knows you like him, and nothing could be more embarrassing than that, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.51,0:05:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I still like you, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.81,0:05:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Just keep that in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.15,0:05:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm remembering pointless things again!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.62,0:05:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,How embarrassing! I'm so embarrassed I could die!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.32,0:05:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I should never have told him!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.82,0:05:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.62,0:05:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave me alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.96,0:05:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll be fine, you'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.69,0:05:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Love is naturally embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.49,0:05:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone loves whilst fighting against embarrassment.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.90,0:05:57.77,Default,,0,0,0,,How did you get together with Nakao-chi, Nobu-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.93,0:05:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.37,0:06:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a winter's day, when the rain was cold as snow...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.11,0:06:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a former gang leader, Nakao-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.35,0:06:16.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard he put twenty delinquents from another school in the hospital all by himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.09,0:06:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my! How scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.36,0:06:30.27,Superscript,,0,0,0,,Stray cat, please take me in
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.34,0:06:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry. I live in an apartment, so I can't take you in.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.35,0:06:46.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You really like milk, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.02,0:06:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,And then one day, I was picked on by some delinquents,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.09,0:06:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,...and the leader of their gang turned out to be...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.63,0:06:57.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I've heard enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.56,0:06:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,And then I put a love letter in his locker...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.70,0:07:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I've heard enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.66,0:07:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Just kidding. just kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.66,0:07:04.23,Default,,0,0,0,,In our last year of middle school, we attended the same cram school and became friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.23,0:07:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Cram school?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.67,0:07:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I said to him, "If only I had a boyfriend like you, Nakao-kun..."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.14,0:07:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,And he said, "If only I had a girlfriend like you, Nobu-chan..."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.14,0:07:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,And then it was like, "So why don't we go out?"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.04,0:07:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,There was no drama involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.91,0:07:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a good thing. I've had enough of drama.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.05,0:07:24.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The person you like likes you back. That's pretty impressive in itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.99,0:07:26.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It's almost a miracle, in fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.79,0:07:27.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Risa...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.49,0:07:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Risa-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.46,0:07:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You too, Chiharu-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.46,0:07:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.99,0:07:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You got your miracle easily enough, and things have gone well with Suzuki-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.70,0:07:39.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You two should be more thankful to God.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.60,0:07:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It-It-It's just me that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.01,0:07:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it! What the hell...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.04,0:07:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this? Alcohol?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.58,0:07:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be fine, Risa-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.18,0:07:51.51,Default,,0,0,0,,He didn't  say that he didn't like you at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.81,0:07:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right, Risa. Just do your best.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.32,0:07:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,But I can't bare my chest!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.52,0:07:59.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You idiot! No one told you to do it literally!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.99,0:08:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I meant mentally bare your chest!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.96,0:08:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Mentally bare my chest?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.63,0:08:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.13,0:08:08.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Reveal the inner breasts that lie deep within your heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.33,0:08:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Mine aren't as big as yours, Nobu-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.30,0:08:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,This has nothing to do with size.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.80,0:08:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Bare them! Go on! Bare them!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.97,0:08:14.30,Overlap,,0,0,0,,I think you should lower your voice...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.84,0:08:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You can do it if you really want to!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.54,0:08:19.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. You're cute too, Risa-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.11,0:08:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Cute?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.51,0:08:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Just use a bit of charm and Otani-kun will be done for.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.45,0:08:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm All-Kyojin...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.05,0:08:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're tall like a model. What's wrong with that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.95,0:08:33.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.96,0:08:37.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Do your best.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.23,0:08:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Believe in miracles.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.10,0:08:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,"Believe in miracles..."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.58,0:08:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I want Otani to fall in love with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.32,0:09:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay! I'll give it a try!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.05,0:09:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The great Christmas plan!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.92,0:09:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.72,0:09:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,First, I'll need to find a Christmas present for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.26,0:09:09.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.99,0:09:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll reveal my chest!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.83,0:09:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.64,0:09:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Otani-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.87,0:09:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,...are you doing anything for Christmas?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.44,0:09:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Disgusting!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.58,0:09:28.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What do you mean, "disgusting"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.91,0:09:31.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Here I am, desperately trying to bare my chest to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.18,0:09:36.89,Default,,0,0,0,,"Chest"?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.42,0:09:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... anyway... are you free for Christmas?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.89,0:09:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,For Christmas?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.76,0:09:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.33,0:09:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.53,0:09:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.83,0:09:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Why does it matter? So you're doing something for Christmas?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.17,0:09:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. My middle school's basketball club is getting together for a Christmas party.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.14,0:10:01.31,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's like the one that Kanzaki-san invited you to last year, but you didn't go?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.48,0:10:03.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, yeah. You remember that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.05,0:10:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,How could I forget?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.75,0:10:09.18,Default,,0,0,0,,T-Then Kanzaki-san will be going too?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.65,0:10:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... Probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.26,0:10:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,She was the manager, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.59,0:10:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't pull that face! It seriously pisses me off!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.20,0:10:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What's your problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.70,0:10:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.47,0:10:28.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm telling you, there's nothing going on between me and that girl, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.54,0:10:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,"That girl"?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.71,0:10:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You're calling her "that girl?" now?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.24,0:10:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my! Have you heard, ma'am?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.31,0:10:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,He just said, "There's nothing going on between me and that girl."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.98,0:10:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to be able to say something like that myself. How cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.11,0:10:40.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What exactly did you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.02,0:10:42.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.89,0:10:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Last year, he hung out with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.63,0:10:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I did make plans with you first, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.60,0:10:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,But that was because of the Umibouzu concert.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.83,0:11:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like he considered me more important than his ex-girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.54,0:11:04.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew that. I knew it, but I was still happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.81,0:11:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Without an Umibouzu ticket, I'm just an All-Kyojin to be rejected.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.85,0:11:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine. Go have a merry Christmas with that girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.75,0:11:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And then, when you just happen to get back together,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.35,0:11:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,...this rejected All-Kyojin will simply stand by silently.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.66,0:11:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Koizumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.13,0:11:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.36,0:11:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Want to come along? To the Christmas party, I mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.77,0:11:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you saying? I don't have anything to do with your middle school.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.57,0:11:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It's open invitation.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.11,0:11:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It is a party, but we'll be playing a bit of basketball too, so the more the merrier, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.98,0:11:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The Nakao couple are coming too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.75,0:11:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.55,0:11:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the first I've heard of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.95,0:11:50.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we can spend Christmas Eve alone together,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.99,0:11:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,...then we can go to the party on Christmas day.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.02,0:11:54.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahh. That's okay then.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.22,0:11:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.06,0:11:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.29,0:11:59.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You're free anyway, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.07,0:12:04.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.91,0:12:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,They said they already ordered a cake.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.38,0:12:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,We're gonna eat it in the gym? Won't we get in trouble?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.45,0:12:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll get in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.28,0:12:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Risa, Risa!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.51,0:12:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Time for the great Christmas plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.28,0:12:23.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Bare your chest, and more forward!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.19,0:12:26.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Chest.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.39,0:12:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Chest.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.89,0:12:31.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Right. Whether it's an ex-girlfriend or whatever, bring it on!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.46,0:12:36.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Using my chest baring power, I'll make Otani fall for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.03,0:12:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Merry Christmas!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.50,0:12:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Otani-senpai and Nakao-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.64,0:12:44.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Merry Christmas!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.34,0:12:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Otani-sempai is as short as always.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.41,0:12:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll smack you for that, damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.18,0:12:52.45,Default,,0,0,0,,The ex-girlfriend isn't here yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.01,0:12:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Otani-sempai, I'm really sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.95,0:12:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Manager Kanzaki couldn't make it today.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.12,0:13:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,So are you two back together yet or what?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.03,0:13:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Geez, you guys! I told you there's nothing going on between us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.26,0:13:11.43,Default,,0,0,0,,And you, don't look so obviously happy about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.64,0:13:14.87,Default,,0,0,0,,So she's not coming?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.80,0:13:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this? What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.21,0:13:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Otani's new girlfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.21,0:13:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.48,0:13:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, n-no. I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.04,0:13:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,She's just an amazon who's in the same class as me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.91,0:13:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,So she's not your girlfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.68,0:13:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,She doesn't look like she would be, huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.65,0:13:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Oww! That hurt!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.05,0:13:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Couldn't you have phrased that better?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.66,0:13:37.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you have a sense of kindness or compassion?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.49,0:13:39.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like I said anything wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.23,0:13:42.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't say anything right, you microbe.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.20,0:13:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Good grief!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.00,0:13:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't bare your chest. You bared your ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.47,0:13:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.57,0:13:52.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, how is this a Christmas party?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.14,0:13:55.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Apparently we'll be having a cake later.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.48,0:13:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.25,0:13:58.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Time for a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.58,0:14:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The sweaty look doesn't suit you at all, darling.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.95,0:14:04.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you guys join in too?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.09,0:14:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't bring my sneakers.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.92,0:14:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't play basketball.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.32,0:14:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,So why couldn't Kanzaki make it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.89,0:14:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,She said something came up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.93,0:14:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,And we were going to go to all that effort to get her and Otani back together too...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.77,0:14:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,But doesn't she have a boyfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.27,0:14:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,We could have just passed that off as a thing of the past...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.31,0:14:27.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-That was close.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.11,0:14:31.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Otani liked Kanzaki-san a lot, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.48,0:14:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It was like he died after they broke up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.05,0:14:39.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It really damaged him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.22,0:14:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It was difficult to watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.66,0:14:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I never heard about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.83,0:14:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought that it would bother Koizumi-san if I mentioned it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.20,0:14:53.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Risa...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.97,0:14:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what were Otani and Kanzaki-san like as a couple?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.77,0:14:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What were they like?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.41,0:15:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, Otani was head over heels in love.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.25,0:15:06.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Before they started going out, he'd get so nervous he could barely speak around her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.28,0:15:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,So we thought it would be funny to lock the two of them in the storeroom together.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.69,0:15:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,After they got out, they started going out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.56,0:15:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Who knows what happened in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.77,0:15:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what could have happened...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.47,0:15:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-Wh-What happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.01,0:15:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,That's payback for before.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.15,0:15:38.95,Default,,0,0,0,,And you two, how long are you planning on drawing out that break for?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.42,0:15:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Gossiping again, were you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.58,0:15:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,We were not!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.49,0:15:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You worry too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.82,0:15:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,In front of someone he likes, he gets so nervous he can barely speak...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.06,0:15:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Risa...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.47,0:16:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I hate Christmas!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.17,0:16:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! What about your chest?! Your chest!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.94,0:16:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I've had enough already!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.38,0:16:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that girl doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.75,0:16:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Otani, are you interested in that girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.92,0:16:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.59,0:16:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, she doesn't seem your type at all, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.72,0:16:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,...she's a fun girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.73,0:16:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Fun, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.90,0:16:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It's rare to find a girl as fun as her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.27,0:16:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, so you kinda like her then?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.00,0:16:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember the chest! Reconsider, Risa! Reconsider!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.14,0:16:43.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I dunno.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.68,0:16:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen up. You bring Otani-kun and...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.79,0:16:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. I'll get everyone to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.73,0:17:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Risa, we'll get yelled at if we eat cake in here, so we're going to eat outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.70,0:17:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.33,0:17:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, before that, could you put this ball back in the storeroom?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.10,0:17:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Why me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.21,0:17:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Just go, just go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.28,0:17:16.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's the ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.05,0:17:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah. Toss it over.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.79,0:17:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, was that a click just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.13,0:17:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't open it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.63,0:17:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yo, this is for real. You got mail.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.17,0:17:38.47,Superscript,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Bare your chest!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.47,0:17:40.94,Superscript,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We'll come and open the door later. Do your best!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.74,0:17:46.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Why...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.41,0:17:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Who was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.48,0:17:50.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobu-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.95,0:17:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What'd she say?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.45,0:17:55.02,Default,,0,0,0,,She told me to bare my chest.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.02,0:17:58.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Don't expose such a dangerous area.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.72,0:18:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah. They got us.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.12,0:18:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh well.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.93,0:18:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,"Oh well"?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.96,0:18:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Otani...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.03,0:18:12.37,Default,,0,0,0,,...when you and Kanzaki-san were locked in the storeroom, you weren't this calm, were you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.11,0:18:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,H-H-H-How do you know about that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.54,0:18:22.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I just heard about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.61,0:18:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Who told you?! I'll kill them!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.45,0:18:26.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you two do?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.95,0:18:28.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What? What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.65,0:18:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you two do?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.69,0:18:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,In this dark room, all alone with Kanzaki-san, what did you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.86,0:18:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing at all, you idiot! We just talked!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.76,0:18:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Considering you were so nervous you couldn't even talk straight,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.83,0:18:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,...what could you two have talked about all alone together?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.80,0:18:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You even know that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.77,0:18:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it, those guys are gonna pay!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.54,0:18:51.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you confess?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.64,0:18:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess it was something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.05,0:18:59.41,Default,,0,0,0,,So you really liked her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.68,0:19:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I already told you...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.99,0:19:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I already told you, that was in the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.56,0:19:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.03,0:19:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.04,0:19:24.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You sure have been crying a lot lately, Koizumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.11,0:19:26.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Who do you think is to blame for that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.81,0:19:27.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.91,0:19:30.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't look so genuinely surprised. Who else could it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.48,0:19:33.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. I guess that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.22,0:19:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Geez, you idiot...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.46,0:19:42.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Miracles can't happen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.06,0:19:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.06,0:19:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,A Christmas present.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.90,0:19:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? For me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.23,0:19:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I brought it on a whim.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.67,0:19:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It's pointless keeping it, so I'll give it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.11,0:20:03.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, they're gloves! I've been wanting some.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.55,0:20:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Good for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.18,0:20:08.45,Default,,0,0,0,,But I didn't get anything for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.75,0:20:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I figured.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.78,0:20:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like I was expecting anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.22,0:20:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,That much?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.09,0:20:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You really like me that much?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.47,0:20:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! Why are you saying that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.27,0:20:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,But you...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.07,0:20:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,But nothing! Stop blabbering pointless things like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.18,0:20:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Hurry up and open the door, Nobu-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.69,0:20:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with that smile?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.12,0:20:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.42,0:20:50.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You're laughing!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.83,0:20:51.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.73,0:20:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Find something funny, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.36,0:20:57.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It is funny, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.61,0:21:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Risa...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.57,0:21:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell is wrong with you?!\N Maybe you really do have a bad personality!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.58,0:21:09.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Funny, funny!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.35,0:21:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut the hell up!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.89,0:21:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It is Christmas, so it'd be nice if a miracle happened to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.28,0:23:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Kanzaki broke up with her boyfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.04,0:23:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,This is bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.67,0:23:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Otani is going to be swept off his feet by his ex-girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.83,0:23:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You're overdoing it with the adrenaline.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.06,0:23:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Lovely Complex ~ Love Com.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.88,0:23:32.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Next: Complete Despair!\N A Love Revival With the Ex?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.82,0:23:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Be sure to watch!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.29,0:23:35.02,Preview Title,,0,0,0,,Complete Despair!\N A Love Revival With the Ex?!
